snippet.title: Aquaman Premiere Cast Arrivals & Autograph Signing - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Dolph Lundgren
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Dolph Lundgren, Patrick Wilson, Director James Wan and composer Rupert Gregon-Williams arrive on the red carpet for their movie based on DC Comics' Aquaman. Signing autographs for the waiting fans at the World Premiere in London's Leicester Square.

Plot: Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and be a hero to the world.
